                     <p class="text-accent mb-4">By averaging the returns for each month over the 25-year period, we can clearly identify historical strengths and weaknesses. The data provides strong evidence for a robust "Santa Claus Rally" in December and confirms the notorious underperformance of the "September Effect."</p>
